summary: This mod adds all thu\'um words into the game.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds all thu\'um words into the game. I hope some modders will find it useful. If you\'ve found any mistake or misspelling then feel free to write about it. I\'ve written them by hadn in about two hours, so it won\'t be surprise if I\'ve mistyped something.

P.S. It\'s my first mod ever, so don\'t be too harsh on me especially if what I\'ve done is pointless. I\'ve done it mostly because I felt like it\'s fun way to learn some new words.

P.P.S. I think I\'ve forgotten to upload the file yesterday. So I uploaded it now. Sorry
author: Keltas
